    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-stlye lean pork patties</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato wedges </strong>and <strong>quick-pickled radish salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop over the <strong>sweet chilli sauce </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
